"by clicking on the tool icon <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref=\"images/"
"toolbox/stock-tool-rect-select-22.png\"/></guiicon> in the ToolBox,"
msgstr ""
"en cliquant sur l'icône de l'outil <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref=\"images/"
