#: src/toolbox/selection/rectangle.xml:136(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/selection/foreground.xml:194(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/selection/ellipse.xml:107(keycap)
#: src/toolbox/selection/ellipse.xml:136(keycap)
